column4: Text
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "876D7CE64AC8C1DBC058E9A2BCEFA397", "Hey, here\'s new info.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "87BB7A374BA538DE1218659DEB7C30ED", "For Fresh or In-Training Digimon, try to repeat the same training.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "23F383D74ABCC722A0FE8BBE2F7F4A49", "Something good will happen.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "F61796164CF69C4C5FA20FAE88AA401B", "Here\'s new info.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "D59F400A4E7A09C78B5B41B7F2775A97", "For Bonus try, if you line up the same pictures, his ability is boosted greatly.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "85D1552D4DE100518915A6A277187EA8", "Ok, i was supposed to talk about Techniques.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "9D1498214B6BC185CAF97A982927942A", "Techniques that an enemy uses, can be mastered if you win a battle.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "E1C40CDD4A5A273F83F2DBB2C0CE80ED", "But Techniques are limited to those wich can be added at that time.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "F6BD6FF140F8B28343A89FA696FC6215", "You can\'t master everything. But battling is the fastest way yo master Techniques.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "3A16640447CCD4E0921346B14998088C", "You can also master though training, but chances are low.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "47951CCD41EA1144E8B43C8FF10E4A76", "When you get smarter, take {Player}\'s classroom and you may learn a Technique.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "D4399C1D4DD11977710650912184E2A4", "Chances of you learning are low, so don\'t expect too much. Train with balance!")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "928389A8498771506CA69287BA026227", "Hey, I\'m Koromon. Jiji told me to tell you about Training.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "13BB9F5142BC0EF28509C69CF5F12CB7", "Wanna ask me something?")

column13: ((22, NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "069470F244406F94D7A56AA8134FF673", "What Training?")),(27, NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "C91A84124C4A1E02AC9D37AEFDFFBFEB", "Teach me how to train")),(36, NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "F08A9B63466798978591EA9C3FAB9F05", "No, nothing")))

column4: NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "EAB0A41046B66E0488FFBFAFE62350DC", "If you train here, you can boost your Digimon\'s abilities.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "8A55CA014180697C6812F492B111EFCD", "Training makes you tired, but you\'ll get more out of it than actual battle.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "9A22D3E14066F6269C4873A9DCF9FAAE", "Also, though very rare, you can master new Techniques.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "241A05E4499C146F1C807E8B8B2C17C5", "I\'ll teach you more about Techniques next time.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "14EEB3C04EA761E44DB7748EB5F2FABC", "There are six training stations near by, and they have signs near by.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "68D09A46456603162339EEBA37E776BA", "Read the signs, and you\'ll know wich abilites you can boost.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "2FFBC7554A79E79630287DA39525EB64", "Depending on your Digimon\'s Specialty, some abilites are boosted more than others.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "4362CC5043834FEC16D6AE9B2C148317", "You won\'t know for sure until you try though.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "A217F87A43DF33ABCA1DB6B4B377BD4D", "After \'Begin\' choose \'Normal\' and train for an one hour.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "E60A16DC4FBFE8CC4A47F1A10C8EF75F", "Oh yeah, I have to tell you about \'Bonus Try\'")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "95837C7E464634B1D51F5DAEFA8CBAAF", "If successful, Bonus Try greatly boosts your power, but little if you fail.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "910108104AD6403B84A073A1C0F63819", "Try it once and you see.")
NSLOCTEXT("[07136849499DB843C8FE33874B1DE8FD]", "4D88AF76481FE0DB509872B4EF8AA3CA", "Well, I\'ll get more new info for you soon.")
